descript.abstract: 1992 Country Boundaries (layer) is a symbolized display presentation of the World Countries 1992 data set. The geographic and attribute data of World Countries 1992 are symbolized to create the layer. All features are symbolized as a single symbol.
descript.purpose: 1992 Country Boundaries (layer) provides a common and useful display of World Countries 1992 for a better understanding of the data set contents. Add this layer to a map to display useful information about the data set and that integrates well with other data set layers.
descript.supplinf: For more information about the data set, see its metadata.
